@page
@{
    Layout = "_LayoutMarketing";
    ViewData["Title"] = "Product roadmap";
    ViewData["Description"] = "What's live now on ePegboard and what we're building next - smarter picking, deeper reports, more tournament formats and in-app payments.";
}

<!-- HERO -->
<section class="page-hero" style="padding:0">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="inner">
      <div class="crumb"><a href="/">Home</a> <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M9 6l6 6-6 6"/></svg> <span>Roadmap</span></div>
      <span class="eyebrow">Product roadmap</span>
      <h1 style="margin-top:10px">What we're building next</h1>
      <p class="lede">We ship features as they are ready, and we prioritise off the back of what clubs tell us. Here is what is live now, and what is coming.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- SHIPPED -->
<section>
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="section-head center"><span class="eyebrow">Live now</span><h2>Already in the web app</h2><p>All of this is running today at <a href="https://play.epegboard.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">play.epegboard.com</a>.</p></div>
    <div class="pill-row" style="justify-content:center">
      <span class="pill"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5"/></svg> Runs in any browser, no install</span>
      <span class="pill"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5"/></svg> Smarter, fairer game picking</span>
      <span class="pill"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5"/></svg> Pick explanations</span>
      <span class="pill"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5"/></svg> Live fairness stats</span>
      <span class="pill"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5"/></svg> Player rating graphs</span>
      <span class="pill"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5"/></svg> Attendance reports &amp; trends</span>
      <span class="pill"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5"/></svg> Handicap tournaments</span>
      <span class="pill"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5"/></svg> Group stages &amp; knockouts</span>
      <span class="pill"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5"/></svg> Live competition standings</span>
      <span class="pill"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5"/></svg> Partnership &amp; team insights</span>
      <span class="pill"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5"/></svg> Member management</span>
      <span class="pill"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.4" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M20 6L9 17l-5-5"/></svg> Payment tracking</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- COMING NEXT -->
<section class="bg-soft">
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="section-head center"><span class="eyebrow">Coming next</span><h2>Roughly in priority order</h2><p>Dates are not fixed. The order reflects what clubs are asking for most.</p></div>
    <div class="steps">
      <div class="step"><div class="n">1</div><h4>Picker enhancements</h4><p>Persistent partner preferences (for league pairs), single-discipline sessions (mixed-only, men's or ladies'), singles support, and continued fairness work on sit-out streaks and carry-over.</p></div>
      <div class="step"><div class="n">2</div><h4>Deeper club reports</h4><p>Court utilisation, match quality and competitiveness, and member-engagement reports, brought together in a redesigned insights hub.</p></div>
      <div class="step"><div class="n">3</div><h4>More tournament formats</h4><p>Singles and team-event tournaments alongside handicap doubles, plus inter-club competitions between clubs running ePegboard.</p></div>
      <div class="step"><div class="n">4</div><h4>In-app payments</h4><p>Collect session fees and subscriptions inside ePegboard, with a cost-split calculator for the night.</p></div>
      <div class="step"><div class="n">5</div><h4>Player self-service</h4><p>Let members check themselves in with a short club code or PIN, taking pressure off the desk on a busy night.</p></div>
      <div class="step"><div class="n">6</div><h4>Phone display polish</h4><p>The web app works on phones today; we are making the smaller-screen experience as good as it is on a tablet or laptop.</p></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- NOTE -->
<section>
  <div class="wrap">
    <div class="callout" style="max-width:820px;margin:0 auto;align-items:center">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M21 15a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H7l-4 4V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h14a2 2 0 0 1 2 2z"/></svg>
      <p>Priorities evolve with feedback and technical constraints. If something here matters to your club, tell us at <a href="mailto:support@epegboard.com">support@epegboard.com</a> - it genuinely helps us prioritise. Desktop-app users: most new work now lands on the web app, and the desktop version stays supported.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- CTA -->
<section class="cta">
  <div class="wrap">
    <h2>Try what's already there</h2>
    <p>Free for 60 days, no card details. See the live features on your own club night.</p>
    <a class="btn btn-ghost btn-lg" style="background:#fff" href="https://play.epegboard.com/signup" target="_blank">Start Free Trial</a>
    <p class="fine">Tablet or laptop-sized screens recommended for the best experience.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- FOOTER -->
